'''Dwarf-road''' refers to two distinctly-different roads:
* [[Dwarf-road of Beleriand]], built by the [[Dwarves]] of the [[Blue Mountains]] to trade with the [[Elves]] of [[Beleriand]].
* Dwarf-road of Mirkwood, also known as the [[Old Forest Road]], built by [[Durin's Folk]] to travel between their kingdoms.
